...............

 -- Scheme Procedure: frame? obj
 -- C Function: scm_frame_p (obj)
     Return `#t' if OBJ is a stack frame.

 -- Scheme Procedure: frame-previous frame
 -- C Function: scm_frame_previous (frame)
